---
import DefaultLayout from '@/layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
---

<DefaultLayout
  title="Nos Services — Courage Formation"
  description="Découvrez tous les services de Courage Formation : création d'organisme de formation, accès EDOF/CPF, certification RNCP/RS, génération de leads et accompagnement marketing."
>
  <main class="section-padding container space-y-20">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-5 max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-8">
      <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-secondary px-3 py-1 text-xs text-secondary-foreground font-medium border border-secondary">
        Nos services
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl tracking-tight">
        Un accompagnement complet pour lancer et développer votre centre de formation
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-base max-w-xl mx-auto leading-7">
        De la création de votre organisme jusqu'à la génération de vos premiers clients — nous sommes à vos côtés à chaque étape.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Services grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

      <a href="/services/creation-organisme-formation" class="rounded-2xl p-6 block group" style="background-color: #fafafa;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <svg class="size-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Création OF</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Lancez votre organisme de formation avec une structure claire, rapide et conforme à la réglementation.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-accent">
          Découvrir <svg class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/acces-edof-cpf" class="rounded-2xl p-6 block group" style="background-color: #fafafa;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <svg class="size-5 text-pink-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 8.25h19.5M2.25 9h19.5m-16.5 5.25h6m-6 2.25h3m-3.75 3h15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 4.5 19.5Z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Accès EDOF / CPF</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Débloquez l'accès au CPF et ouvrez de nouvelles opportunités de financement pour vos formations.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-accent">
          Découvrir <svg class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/certification-rncp-rs" class="rounded-2xl p-6 block group" style="background-color: #fafafa;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <svg class="size-5 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 3.741-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0 1 12 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 0 0 6.75 15.75v-1.5" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Création RNCP / RS</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Développez des formations certifiantes à forte valeur et différenciez votre offre sur le marché.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-accent">
          Découvrir <svg class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/generation-leads" class="rounded-2xl p-6 block group" style="background-color: #fafafa;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <svg class="size-5 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18 9 11.25l4.306 4.306a11.95 11.95 0 0 1 5.814-5.518l2.74-1.22m0 0-5.94-2.281m5.94 2.28-2.28 5.941" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Génération de Leads</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Attirez des prospects qualifiés et remplissez vos sessions de formation grâce à une machine d'acquisition.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-accent">
          Découvrir <svg class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/marketing-croissance" class="rounded-2xl p-6 block group" style="background-color: #fafafa;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <svg class="size-5 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Marketing & Croissance</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Site web, image de marque, acquisition : tout pour accélérer votre développement et vous démarquer.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-accent">
          Découvrir <svg class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/services/accompagnement" class="rounded-2xl p-6 block group" style="background-color: #fafafa;">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-3">
          <svg class="size-5 text-red-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.8" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0ZM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0 1 14.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0 1 12 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632Z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-sm group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Accompagnement</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">Un partenaire expert à vos côtés à chaque étape de votre croissance, de la création au passage à l'échelle.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-accent">
          Découvrir <svg class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" /></svg>
        </p>
      </a>

    </div>

    <!-- Stats band -->
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-border bg-muted/30 py-10 px-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold">+200</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">organismes créés</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold">2–4 sem.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">délai moyen de création d'OF</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold">100%</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">clé en main</p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold">98%</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">taux de satisfaction</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-4 pb-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Pas sûr par où commencer ?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm max-w-md mx-auto">Réservez un diagnostic gratuit de 15 minutes — nous vous guidons vers le service qui correspond à votre situation.</p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-foreground px-7 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-background hover:bg-foreground/85 transition-colors"
      >
        Réserver un diagnostic gratuit
      </a>
    </div>

  </main>
</DefaultLayout>
